'''''côf''''' is a [[Sindarin]] word meaning "bay".<ref name=VT>{{VT|42a}}, p. 15</ref>

==Examples==
*''[[Bay of Belfalas#Other names|'''Côf''' Belfalas]]'' ("Bay of Belfalas")<ref name=VT/>

==Other versions of the legendarium==
In an early text called the ''[[Noldorin Word-lists]]'', there appears the word '''''cú''''' ("bay, cove").<ref>{{PE|13}}, "[[Noldorin Word-lists]]", entry '''cú''', p. 141</ref><ref>{{webcite |author= |articleurl= https://eldamo.org/content/words/word-3698044421.html|articlename= S. côf ''n''.|dated= |website= Eldamo|accessed= 22 December 2025|archiveurl= |archivename= |archivedate=}}</ref>

